{"type": "article", "id": 44542, "title": "把这张纸卷一卷，就成了一盏灯｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-27T22:52:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 43553, "name": "nendo"}, {"id": 43554, "name": "竹尾"}, {"id": 43555, "name": "Francesc Moret Studio"}, {"id": 43556, "name": "Pizza Market"}, {"id": 43557, "name": "AglC"}, {"id": 43558, "name": "ShadeCraft"}, {"id": 43559, "name": "Maddalena Bearzi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 162, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170827193848DIxO8kJi4Y2Z351g.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Paper-torch by nendo et al.</h3><p>还记得那个只要卷起来就能<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27811.html\">发光的书签</a>吗？最近，专门研发这种纸上电路的日本公司 <a href=\"https://agic.cc/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">AgIC</a> 与设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 以及造纸公司<a href=\"http://www.takeo.co.jp/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">竹尾</a>联手打造了一款卷起来就能用的灯饰 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/paper-torch/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paper-torch</a>。它由竹屋开发的选票用纸ユポ制成，这种纸不仅光滑柔韧，还具有不错的载墨性。纸张两面都印有排布成格子状的电路，一面贴着 7 个小型 LED 灯。灯光的强弱则由所卷起的圆筒直径所决定，越小光线就越明亮且集中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708271939166uNjwhr8aJApIFcG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193915FGLvRIsPCDqAuZOT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708271939150Dz5LdeS6qhQPEJV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193916xdKWSsf9a73BrApU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rainbow Glass by Urban Outfitters</h3><p>小酌时觉得杯子太过单调？美国零售品牌 <a href=\"https://www.urbanoutfitters.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Urban Outfitters</a> 推出的彩虹底玻璃杯系列可以让你体验把彩虹一口喝掉的感觉。这个系列包含成对出售的香槟杯以及高低两款钻石杯，就算只是倒入普通的水也挺好看的。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.urbanoutfitters.com/search?q=rainbow+glass\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价从 16 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017082719393331nAiUMF7eBj8Cgy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.524000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193933NJqSRxavryt3Mb2L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193933G6nUT5WjQOpI9KPH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sunflower by ShadeCraft</h3><p>想象一下这样的场景：去沙滩度假时，你头顶的遮阳伞会边悉数吸收太阳能边为你提供各种语音服务，当太阳变化角度时，它还能够跟着移动。这个被称为户外 AI 的智能遮阳伞由新西兰科技公司 <a href=\"http://shadecraft.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ShadeCraft</a> 研发，曾在今年的 CES 大会上做过展示。它内置有 360 度的摄像头、可调节的照明系统、扬声器以及多个充电插口，号称可以在仅依靠电池的情况下运作 72 小时以上。目前，它还处于概念设计阶段，尚未正式投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193958QHIJPRayrFjsUo7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639364\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193958tBYyle8zsQxUvgki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193958wHCIsm7FlLREDJdZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827193958APzY4xwfOWGCnvH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539120\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jewellery by Maddalena Bearzi</h3><p>作为洛杉矶非盈利组织“海洋保护学会”（Ocean Conservation Society）的主席，意大利海洋生物学家 Maddalena Bearzi 博士经常出海拜访她的动物朋友们。以自己最熟悉的海洋生态为灵感来源，她开始将回收来的金属、旧首饰以及石头打造成独一无二的海洋首饰。如果你对把海底世界戴在身上感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.maddalenabearzi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>查看她的作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708271942356s5nx0AEMkVN1UlB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708271942367ryIzCE6Yntgljqh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708271942357tJuWNT56ELFbc8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194235N0bE3TWg1kDCat6U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194236bfy70C1OudjRaoZs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pizza Market by Francesc Moret Studio</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/33599.html\">街头风披萨盒</a>吗？由西班牙设计工作室 <a href=\"http://francescmoret.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Francesc Moret Studio</a> 为披萨连锁品牌 <a href=\"http://pizzamarket.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pizza Market</a> 五周年庆而设计的营销主题同样不依靠明亮的配色激发食欲，反而显得有点酷。考虑到这是一套全球统一的方案，设计团队决定拿最通行的语言——音乐来做文章。他们选择了五首歌曲，将披萨相关的元素融入到文字和图案设计当中，表现出对披萨的渴望：比如《Satisfaction》的歌名就排列成了一片披萨的模样，on 处还有被咬过的痕迹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194046ZGMEtNCL6IJ4DzPp.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194045nJCsVzm0h2d4BtA7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194045IlCuTwXgQq1iap6L.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194045mnouwKY06kHAlsOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fake shadows by Damon Belanger</h3><p>你上一次走在街头留意事物的影子是什么时候？对于美国加州红木城（Redwood）的居民而言，最近一段时间各种物体映在街上的影子还真的很难无视：邮箱变成了等着投喂信件的怪兽、长椅原来是一头回眸的小动物、停车计时器上其实还蹲着猴子……这些假影子其实是市政府邀请旧金山艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.damonbelanger.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Damon Belanger</a> 创作的，希望借此为日常生活注入一些乐趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194105ECLZRt2oQ9uVyDSM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194105kG4c9LdWOoSwbThz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170827194105qsR5vFr7XI2CPufM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708271941060Zpx7rGPVYJoqD4M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}